snippet.title: Asphalt Legends Unite - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Asphalt Legends Unite will be arriving to Asphalt 9: Legends on July 17th.

This will be the first step in the evolution of the series and the first expansion in its history.

Check out the trailer and stay tuned for more news tomorrow!

Head over to the new Asphalt Legends Unite website for more details:
https://www.asphaltlegendsunite.com

Play Asphalt 9: http://gmlft.co/A9YTDL

To get the latest news from Asphalt, follow us on:
Facebook Asphalt 9: https://www.facebook.com/Asphalt9Legends/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/asphalt
Instagram:https://www.instagram.com/asphaltgames
Discord: https://discord.gg/asphalt9
